data.description: Modern custom ranch home on nearly an acre. Approx $300K renovation(inc lifetime metal roof) completed by award winning designer-builder in 2020.  Separate in-law apartment with spacious bedroom and walk-in closet has private entrance, full kitchen and dedicated central AC, water heater and washer/dryer. The apartment is currently being used as Airbnb while owner’s family enjoys the 5 bedroom and 4 full bath main residence. Outdoor kitchen with grill, pool and huge fully fenced backyard with mature fruit trees (avocado, mango, coconut, bananas, palm dates and suriname cherries).  Riding mower and lawn equipment also convey. This home is zoned for A rated schools elementary through high school.  Three separate AC zones, two in main house and one for apartment, all less than five years old.
